name: Tempsy-Violation-Visualization
body:
Welcome to TemPsy-Violation-Visualization
==========

TemPsy-Violation-Visualization is an interactive visualization tool for navigating and analyzing *TemPsy* violations. The tools has been developed by [Wei Dou](http://people.svv.lu/dou), at the [SVV lab](http://www.svv.lu) of the [University of Luxembourg](http://wwwen.uni.lu).
